graph TD
    A[User types https://www.google.com<br/>and presses Enter] --> B[DNS Resolution]
    B -->|Returns IP: 142.250.80.46| C[Browser initiates request<br/>to IP:443 HTTPS port]
    C --> D[Traffic Encrypted<br/>via HTTPS/SSL]
    D --> E[Firewall<br/>Security Check]
    E -->|Traffic allowed| F[Load Balancer<br/>Distributes request]
    F --> G[Web Server<br/>Receives request]
    G --> H[Application Server<br/>Generates web page]
    H --> I[Database<br/>Queries user data]
    I -->|Returns data| H
    H -->|Sends generated page| G
    G -->|Sends response| F
    F --> E
    E --> D
    D -->|Encrypted response| C
    C --> J[Browser displays<br/>Google homepage]
